ActFederal Courts Act
SubjectFederal Court of Canada ** (6) Commissioners for administering oaths **
PrecisOrder directing that a COMMISSION do issue under the Great Seal of Canada empowering six officers of the Courts Administration Service to administer oaths and to take and receive affidavits, declarations and solemn affirmations within or outside Canada in or concerning any proceeding had or to be had in the FEDERAL COURTS.
